ugh Italy (opens in a new tab)\" href=\"https:\/\/www.saltinourhair.com\/italy\/italy-travel-guide\/\" target=\"_blank\">2-week trip through Italy<\/a> isn&#x2019;t complete without a proper swim in the Saturnia hot springs. Bring your towel and drinking water so you won&#x2019;t get dehydrated but change in your hotel or car. There are no changing facilities at these hot springs in Tuscany.<\/p>\n\n\n<div class=\"block-link block-link--readmore \">\n                <div class=\"block-link__container\">\n\n                    <div class=\"salt-icon__container\">\n                        <span class=\"salt-icon salt-icon--readmore\"><\/span>\n                        <svg class=\"icon icon-round-shape\"><use xlink:href=\"#icon-round-shape\"><\/use><\/svg>\n                    <\/div>\n\n                    <p><strong>Read:<\/strong> <a href=\"https:\/\/www.saltinourhair.com\/italy\/italy-travel-guide\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\" aria-label=\"2-week Italy Travel Guide (opens in a new tab)\">2-week Italy Travel Guide<\/a><\/p>\n\n\n                <\/div>\n            <\/div>\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-gallery has-nested-images columns-default is-cropped\">\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large\"><div class=\"image-wrapper\"><div class=\"fake-image\"><\/div><noscript><img src=\"https:\/\/saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/05\/things-to-do-saturnia-hotpools-1-648x810.jpg\" alt=\"things to do saturnia hotpools\"><\/noscript><img width=\"270\" height=\"338\" alt=\"things to do saturnia hotpools\" class=\"wp-image-14063 lazypreload\" data-sizes=\"(max-width: 648px) 100vw, 648px\" data-srcset=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/05\/23135611\/things-to-do-saturnia-hotpools-1-648x810.jpg 648w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/05\/23135611\/things-to-do-saturnia-hotpools-1-300x375.jpg 300w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/05\/23135611\/things-to-do-s